data.description: End Unit Townhouse in "The Pines at Pennridge"! The covered front entry with partial stone front is the first of many fine features you will find in this home. The entrance foyer with tile floor welcomes you to the first floor. The eat in kitchen has a ton of cabinet and counter space and a pass through opening to the dining room. The formal dining room has hardwood floors and is the perfect spot for hosting family and holiday dinners. The spacious living room has sliders to the rear patio and two car parking. A coat closet and powder room complete this floor. The second floor has three bedrooms and two full baths. The primary bedroom has a ceiling fan, walk-in closet and full bath. The second bedroom has a ceiling fan and ample closet space. The third bedroom can also be used as a home office. The full finished basement has an outside exit . Basement includes a wet Bar, Family Room and a special nook for a possible office area! Rear patio for outdoor entertaining and lots of parking on the side street in addition to the rear parking. It is minutes to parks, trails, shopping, elementary and high school.  Close to Rt 309, 563, 113 and 313!
